# Shared by all image builds: Dockerfiles copy the workspace manifests needed
# for a filtered root install (turbo prune is banned because it corrupts
# bun.lock). Keep the build context to tracked-ish sources.
.git
.turbo
node_modules
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
**/.cache
**/.venv
**/target
**/*.log
.claude
sandbox
packages/docs
